properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 1 at 3:04AM EST until February 2 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds around 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 4 to 7 feet expected.

* WHERE...From Bonita Beach to Suwannee River FL out 60 NM.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 7 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM THIS EVENING TO 7 AM EST SUNDAY
